# About this Guide

I will be reading the [Oracle Database 26ai Concepts Guide](https://docs.oracle.com/en/database/oracle/oracle-database/26/cncpt/index.html) and asking myself questions.
These questions will be answered here and shared via linkedin and potentially youtube.

# Goal

Share knowledge with others throughout the database concepts guide. This could serve as a quick lookup for many people, serving as a reminder of Oracle syntax and some features others may not know about. 

